        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR3c0004-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-1a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:51:07.871+09:00">秦孝公在策畫國家大計。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:51:20.879+09:00">公孫鞅、廿龍、杜摯三位大夫陪侍在旁，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:51:45.456+09:00">共同思考世事的憂化，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:51:56.616+09:00">商討膠正法律的根源，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:52:34.61+09:00">研求役使人民的方法。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:57:46.626+09:00">孝公說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:58:00.681+09:00">「繼承先君做了國君而不忽略國家大事，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:58:16.737+09:00">是做國君應有的道理．</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:58:48.175+09:00">旅行法令務須表現人主的長處，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:58:58.208+09:00">是臣子應有的行爲。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:59:07.938+09:00">現在我想修改法令來治理國家，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:59:15.513+09:00">變更禮個來敎化百姓，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-2a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T20:59:32.21+09:00">但恐怕天下會批評我。」</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:01:35.395+09:00">公孫鞅說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:02:10.619+09:00">「臣聽說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:02:17.788+09:00">『游移不定的行爲是無法完成的，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:02:25.737+09:00">游移不決的事項是不會成功的。』</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:02:32.019+09:00">君上趕快下定變法的決心，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:02:39.7+09:00">一定不要顧慮天下人的批評。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:02:47.366+09:00">而且有超越常人的行爲的人，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:03:21.009+09:00">必然被世人議論;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:03:30.42+09:00">有獨特見解的人，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-3a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:03:38.527+09:00">必定被一般人詆毀。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:03:47.548+09:00">俗語說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:03:55.755+09:00">『愚笨的人事情做成功了還不知道其中的道理，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:04:04.201+09:00">明智的人在事情還沒有發生之前就已經觀察出來。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:04:13.298+09:00">一般人民不可與之謀晝創始，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:04:21.797+09:00">然而可以與之樂享成功。』</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:04:28.508+09:00">郭偃的法令說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:05:09.442+09:00">『講論高深道德的人</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:05:17.006+09:00">不與憔俗相和，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:05:39.662+09:00">成就偉大功業的人</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-4a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:05:52.372+09:00">不與眾人相謀畫。』</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:06:02.351+09:00">法，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:06:08.217+09:00">是用來惠愛人民的；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:06:16.633+09:00">禮，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:06:22.662+09:00">是用來便利行癢的。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:06:30.211+09:00">所以聖人假如可使國家富強，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:06:36.43+09:00">不遵行舊日的法度；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:06:42.312+09:00">假如能有利於人民，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-5a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:06:44.155+09:00">不依循蕉日的禮制。」</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:07:41.374+09:00">孝公說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:09:23.064+09:00">"好。“</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:09:34.644+09:00">廿龍說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:09:41.897+09:00">「不然。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:09:53.363+09:00">臣聽說過，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:10:03.603+09:00">聖人不違反民性而施行敎化，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:10:13.445+09:00">明智的人不改變法度而治理國家。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:10:20.94+09:00">順著人民的本性而施行敎化的，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:10:27.879+09:00">不必辛勞而事功就能完成．，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:10:37.096+09:00">依據舊日法度而治理的，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-6a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:10:43.603+09:00">官吏嫺熟法度而人民也感到習慣。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:10:50.093+09:00">現在如變更法制，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:10:56.342+09:00">不依循秦國的舊法，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:11:04.119+09:00">改變禮制來敎化人民，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:11:08.645+09:00">臣恐天下人會批評君上，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:11:14.504+09:00">希望君上仔細地加以考暈。」</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:11:46.934+09:00">公孫鞅說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:11:51.086+09:00">「先生所說的，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:11:57.481+09:00">是世俗一般人的說法。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:12:04.243+09:00">平常人習慣於舊日的習俗，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-7a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:12:40.401+09:00">學者溺於自己所學過的那一套．，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:12:47.466+09:00">這兩種人都只能做官遵守法度，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:12:59.525+09:00">不可以跟他們謀畫一般法度外的大事。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:13:44.156+09:00">夏、商、周三代各有不同的禮制，都稱王於天下；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:13:48.114+09:00">五霸各有不同的法度，也都稱霸於天下。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:13:56.182+09:00">所以明智的人制定法度，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:14:00.46+09:00">而愚味的人為去度所局限．，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:14:10.076+09:00">賢能的人更改禮制，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:14:17.915+09:00">而一般人則為禮制所拘束。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:14:46.801+09:00">爲禮制所拘束的人，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:14:51.688+09:00">不可以跟他議論大事．，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:14:59.482+09:00">爲法度所局限的人，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:15:04.513+09:00">不可以跟他討論變革。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-8a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:15:07.226+09:00">君上請不必再游移不決了。」</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:15:42.74+09:00">杜摯說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:15:47.774+09:00">「臣聽說，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:15:54.537+09:00">利盆不到一百倍，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:16:02.111+09:00">不改髮法度，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:16:06.494+09:00">功效不到十倍，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:16:12.79+09:00">不改製器物。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:16:16.228+09:00">臣聽說師行古法的沒有過錯，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:16:24.327+09:00">遵循莓禮的不會有偏邪。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-9a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:17:04.301+09:00">希望君上好好計議一下。」</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:17:16.072+09:00">公孫鞅說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:17:23.314+09:00">「前代各有不同的敎化，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:17:27.77+09:00">應效法那一代？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:17:38.364+09:00">古代帝王不重複再現，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:17:46.292+09:00">應遵循那－種禮制？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:17:55.977+09:00">伏羲、砷農，敎化人民而不實行懲罰；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:18:02.501+09:00">黃帝、堯、舜，徵罰人民而不流於凶暴。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:18:14.925+09:00">到了周文王、武王，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:18:21.39+09:00">各自切合時代的情況而制定法度，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-10a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:18:30.566+09:00">順應事實的需要而制定鵐制。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:18:46.764+09:00">禮法制度，因著時代的情況而訂定．，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:18:54.958+09:00">法制命令，各自順應時代之所宜；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:19:05.403+09:00">兵器鎧甲弓矢，各自便於它特殊的功用。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:19:13.461+09:00">臣所以說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:19:41.833+09:00">『治理天下不是只有一種方法，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:19:46.628+09:00">對國家有利卽不必師法古代。』</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:20:07.455+09:00">商湯、周武王統有天下，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:20:13.745+09:00">不全遵循古法而興起．，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:20:19.651+09:00">商紂、夏桀的覆滅，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-11a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:20:26.153+09:00">不是因更改禮制而亡國。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:20:34.108+09:00">如此看來，與古代相反的不能說必然是錯的，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:20:40.024+09:00">遵循舊禮的也不是全都是對的。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:20:40.378+09:00">君上請不必再游移不決了。」</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:21:29.089+09:00">孝公說：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:21:35.934+09:00">「很好。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:21:50.05+09:00">寡人聽說住在隱僻里巷的人少見多怪，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-12a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:22:47.867+09:00">識見不廣的人好作無意義的爭辯。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-13a.1" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:22:58.829+09:00">愚昧的人感到歡笑的事，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-13a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:23:08.271+09:00">明智的人感到悲哀；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-13a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:23:15.265+09:00">狂妄的人感到快樂的事，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-13a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:23:27.246+09:00">賢明的人感到砭傷，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-13a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:23:38.811+09:00">世人爲了怕受世俗的譏議而受拘束，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-13a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:23:39.188+09:00">寡人則不再游移了。」</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3c0004_tls_001-13a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-06-01T21:24:17.619+09:00">於是就頒布開墾荒地的法令。</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
